Name: A Bakers Dozen!
Description: Take Photos of 13 Gudetama - Use the Camera tool to take photos. The camera is collected after the side-quest Gudetama Snap, after reaching Friendship level 1 with Pochacco

Name: A New Home
Description: Open the Nature Preserve - Completed during the quest Open the Nature Preserve

Name: Aquatic Challenge
Description: Craft the Gold Reef Trophy - Complete all the Challenge Courses in Rainbow Reef to get the Crafting Plans for the Gold Reef Trophy.

Name: Baking Bliss
Description: Unlock 20 recipes at the Oven - The oven is located in Seaside Resort Plaza in Hello Kitty's Cafe. You can make a bunch of recipes using Flour.

Name: Behind the Waterfall
Description: The Hidden Meadow - Enter the Merry Meadow for the first time in the quest Curious Caverns

Name: Bog Champ
Description: Restore the Spooky Swamp - Completed during the quest Re-Haunt the Swamp

Name: Candy Connoisseur
Description: Unlock 10 Recipes at the Candy Cloud Station - The Candy Cloud Station is located in Cloud Island. Recipes are made using Candy Clouds as the main ingredient.

Name: Critter Master
Description: Catch 100 Critters - Use the Net tool to catch critters in each area. You can earn the Net during the quest Open the Nature Preserve.

Name: Definitely Haunted
Description: Restore the Haunted Mansion - Completed during the quest Re-Haunt the Swamp

Name: Delicious Desserts
Description: Unlock 16 Recipes at the Dessert Boat - The Dessert Boat is located within the Dessert Boat restaurant in Gemstone Mountain. Recipes are made using Cactus Cream.

Name: Dinosaurs Not Included
Description: Open the Resort Gate with Chococat - Completed during the quest Power Up the Gate

Name: Dozens Surely!
Description: Take Photos of 120 Gudetama - Use the Camera tool to take photos. Gudetama are scattered across all regions.

Name: Egg-cellent Chef
Description: Unlock 14 Recipes at the Egg Pan Station - The Egg Pan Station is crafted after completing the quest An Egg-cellent Pan. Recipes are made with eggs.

Name: Everyone is Welcome
Description: Have 20 Visitors at 5 Stars - Repair Visitor Cabins to have Visitors stay. Complete their Requests to boost their Star Rating.

Name: Everyone's Bestie
Description: Become Best Friends with 15 Characters - Increase Friendships by gifting gifts daily + completing quests with characters around the islands.

Name: Excellent Espresso
Description: Unlock 13 recipes at the Espresso Machine - The Espresso Machine is located in the Comedy Club within Rainbow Reef. Recipes are made with Candlenut.

Name: Floating Challenge
Description: Craft the Gold Cloud Trophy - Complete all the Challenge Courses in Cloud Island to get the Crafting Plans for the Gold Cloud Trophy.

Name: Floral Challenge
Description: Craft the Gold Meadow Trophy - Complete all the Challenge Courses in Merry Meadow to get the Crafting Plans for the Gold Meadow Trophy.

Name: Floral Pattern
Description: Obtain a patterned flower - Flowers are grown in Merry Meadow by planting seeds + waiting for the flower to bloom. To collect, approach + press the hand icon or E.

Name: Flower Collector
Description: Obtain 10 unique Flower Types - Flowers are grown in Merry Meadow by planting seeds + waiting for the flower to bloom. To collect, approach + press the hand icon or E.

Name: For the Love of Baking
Description: Cook 100 recipes - Prepare any recipe using the Oven in Hello Kitty's Cafe, 100 times.

Name: Friendship Forever
Description: Freed Big Challenges from his Icy Statis + Re-united TOPHAT with his Best Friend - Completed during the quest A Challenging Rescue

Name: Friendships Restored
Description: Reunite the Island Spirit with her Best Friends

Name: Happy Hattery
Description: Put a Hat on a Null - Interact with any Null + choose from any available hats in your Inventory to give it to them.

Name: Happy Landing!
Description: Another Happy Landing! - After completing the quest Happy Landings

Name: Haunted
Description: Fall through the floor of the Haunted Mansion - Fall through a trap door while completing the quest Re-Haunt the Swamp

Name: Hello Bestie!
Description: Become Best Friends with Hello Kitty - Reach Friendship level 25 with Hello Kitty

Name: Master Angler
Description: Catch 100 Fish - Use the Fishing Rod tool to catch fish in any region. The Fishing Rod is collected after completing the side-quest Keep It Reel when reaching Badtz-Maru Friendship level 3.

Name: Master of the Ruins
Description: Complete 20 Puzzle Rooms - Puzzle Rooms are temple-like structures spread through each region of the map. They usually contain Power Crystals or chests.

Name: Mermaids are Real
Description: Activate the Mermaidifier - Completed during the quest Comic Relief

Name: Nap Time
Description: Use a bed to change the time of day - Place a bed in your Cabin + interact with it to sleep + change the time of day.

Name: New Heights
Description: A Paradise in the Clouds - Enter Cloud Island for the first time in the quest Stargazing

Name: Open for Visits
Description: Unlock a Visitor Cabin - Visitor Cabins are unlocked by interacting with the signposts in the front of them + using Strawberry Crates for My Melody to repair them.

Name: Piza Perfection
Description: Unlock 11 recipes at the Pizza Oven - The Pizza Oven is located on Mount Hothead. Recipes are made with Dough.

Name: Rage Mode
Description: Ignited the Volcano with Retsuo's Rage - Completed during the quest Fire Up the Volcano

Name: Reef Revival
Description: Fully restore Rainbow Reef - Completed during the quest Reef Revival

Name: Regional Explorer
Description: Reaching every Region on Friendship Island - Friendship Island is made up of 5 regions -- Seaside Resort, Spooky Swamp, Rainbow Reef, Gemstone Mountain, + Mount Hothead. You'll venture to each within the main story quests.

Name: Rocky Challenge
Description: Craft the Gold Gemstone Trophy - Complete all the Challenge Courses in Gemstone Mountain to get the Crafting Plans for the Gold Gemstone Trophy.

Name: Soda Satisfaction
Description: Unlock 14 recipes at the Soda Fountain

Name: Superb Gift Giver
Description: Give 50 3-Star Gifts - Each character has different "Liked" items. Give Gifts that meet each one of their "Liked" items to make the Gift 3-Stars.

Name: Swampy Challenge
Description: Craft the Gold Swamp Trophy - Complete all the Challenge Courses in Spooky Swamp to get the Crafting Plans for the Gold Swamp Trophy.

Name: Swing Partners
Description: Reboot the Dance Hall band - Completed during the quest Bring Back the Swing

Name: Through Thick + Thin
Description: Have a character follow you to the lowest trench + tallest peak - To have someone follow you, ask them to help you out in dialogue with them or use the Phone "Call a Friend" app. The lowest trench is in Rainbow Reef area while diving + the tallest peak is the top of Icy Peak.

Name: Time for Milk
Description: Have Milk as a 5 Star Visitor

Name: Traveling Party
Description: Companion with one of your friends - Unlock the opportunity to companion with a character by increasing their Friendships. Then, ask them to help you out in dialogue with them or use the Phone "Call a Friend" app to make them your companion.

Name: Tropical Challenge
Description: Craft the Gold Seaside Trophy - Complete all the Challenge Courses in Seaside Resort to get the Crafting Plans for the Gold Seaside Trophy.

Name: True Gamer
Description: Play All the Mini Games Around Friendship Island - Mini Games are run by Nulls in each region of the map. Give them Game Tickets (collected around the ground of the map) to play the Mini Game.

Name: Vacation Hot Spot
Description: Repair twenty five visitor cabins - Approach Visitor Cabins + interact with the signposts out front to repair them with Strawberry Crates.

Name: Volcanic Challenge
Description: Craft the Gold Hothead Trophy - Complete all the Challenge Courses in Mount Hothead to get the Crafting Plans for the Gold Hothead Trophy.

Description: One free ticket use per day

Name: Tophat - Level 9 - Pickup Glitch

Name: Tuxedosam - Level 13 - Negotiator
Description: Increases chance to get extra item when shopping

Name: Usahana - Level 4 - Chef's Kiss
Description: Increases chance of getting an extra item when cooking with the Chef's station

Name: Wish Me Mell - Level 11 - Master Gardener
Description: Increases chance of getting a bonus seed when turning flowers into seed packets

Name: Wish Me Mell - Level 13 - Precision Play
Description: Reduces movement speed of the floating prizes in Crane Craze
